     fhir:status [ fhir:v "extensions" ] ;
     fhir:div "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p><b>Generated Narrative: PlanDefinition</b><a name=\"RecommendationCollectionVentilatedCOVID19patients\"> </a></p><div style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: #d9e0e7; padding: 6px; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid #8da1b4; border-radius: 5px; line-height: 60%\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px\">Resource PlanDefinition &quot;RecommendationCollectionVentilatedCOVID19patients&quot; </p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px\">Profile: <a href=\"file:///github/workspace/output/StructureDefinition-recommendation.html\">Recommendation</a></p></div><p><b>knowledgeCapability</b>: computable</p><p><b>knowledgeRepresentationLevel</b>: structured</p><blockquote><p><b>Action Combination Method</b></p><blockquote><p><b>url</b></p><code>method</code></blockquote><p><b>value</b>: Exactly <span style=\"background: LightGoldenRodYellow; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid khaki\"> (<a href=\"file:///github/workspace/output/CodeSystem-cs-action-combination-method.html\">Action Combination Method</a>#exactly)</span></p><blockquote><p><b>url</b></p><code>threshold</code></blockquote><p><b>value</b>: 1</p></blockquote><p><b>url</b>: <code>https://www.netzwerk-universitaetsmedizin.de/fhir/codex-celida/guideline/covid19-inpatient-therapy/recommendation/covid19-ventilation-plan-peep</code></p><p><b>version</b>: 1.0</p><p><b>name</b>: RecommendationCollection36-a</p><p><b>title</b>: PEEP Intervention for Population: Ventilated COVID-19 Patients</p><p><b>type</b>: Workflow Definition <span style=\"background: LightGoldenRodYellow; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid khaki\"> (<a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/5.3.0/CodeSystem-plan-definition-type.html\">PlanDefinitionType</a>#workflow-definition)</span></p><p><b>status</b>: active</p><p><b>experimental</b>: true</p><p><b>date</b>: 2022-02-14</p><p><b>publisher</b>: Deutsche Gesellschaft für Internistische Intensivmedizin und Notfallmedizin e.V. (DGIIN)</p><p><b>description</b>: Für die orientierende Einstellung des PEEP bei COVID-19 sollte die FiO2/PEEP-Tabelle des ARDS-Networks berücksichtigt werden. Durch ein engmaschiges Monitoring kann der PEEP der individuellen Situation des Patienten angepasst werden.</p><blockquote><p><b>action</b></p><p><b>title</b>: PEEP_Intervention_Plan_FiO2_0.0</p><p><b>description</b>: PEEP Intervention plan for COVID-19 patients, inspiratory oxygen fraction currently 0.0 - 0.39</p><p><b>code</b>: Guideline-based Care <span style=\"background: LightGoldenRodYellow; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid khaki\"> (<a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/uv/cpg/STU1/CodeSystem-cpg-common-process.html\">CPG Common Process</a>#guideline-based-care)</span></p><p><b>selectionBehavior</b>: one-or-more</p><p><b>definition</b>: <a href=\"PlanDefinition-VentilatedCOVID19patientsInterventionPlan-fio2-point0.html\">PEEP Intervention plan for COVID-19 patients, inspiratory oxygen fraction currently 0.0 - 0.39</a></p></blockquote><blockquote><p><b>action</b></p><p><b>title</b>: PEEP_Intervention_Plan_FiO2_0.4</p><p><b>description</b>: PEEP Intervention plan for COVID-19 patients, inspiratory oxygen fraction currently 0.4 - 0.49</p><p><b>code</b>: Guideline-based Care <span style=\"background: LightGoldenRodYellow; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid khaki\"> (<a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/uv/cpg/STU1/CodeSystem-cpg-common-process.html\">CPG Common Process</a>#guideline-based-care)</span></p><p><b>selectionBehavior</b>: one-or-more</p><p><b>definition</b>: <a href=\"PlanDefinition-VentilatedCOVID19patientsInterventionPlan-fio2-point4.html\">PEEP Intervention plan for COVID-19 patients, inspiratory oxygen fraction currently 0.4 - 0.49</a></p></blockquote><blockquote><p><b>action</b></p><p><b>title</b>: PEEP_Intervention_Plan_FiO2_0.5</p><p><b>description</b>: PEEP Intervention plan for COVID-19 patients, inspiratory oxygen fraction currently 0.5 - 0.59</p><p><b>code</b>: Guideline-based Care <span style=\"background: LightGoldenRodYellow; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid khaki\"> (<a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/uv/cpg/STU1/CodeSystem-cpg-common-process.html\">CPG Common Process</a>#guideline-based-care)</span></p><p><b>selectionBehavior</b>: one-or-more</p><p><b>definition</b>: <a href=\"PlanDefinition-VentilatedCOVID19patientsInterventionPlan-fio2-point5.html\">PEEP Intervention plan for COVID-19 patients, inspiratory oxygen fraction currently 0.5 - 0.59</a></p></blockquote><blockquote><p><b>action</b></p><p><b>title</b>: PEEP_Intervention_Plan_FiO2_0.6</p><p><b>description</b>: PEEP Intervention plan for COVID-19 patients, inspiratory oxygen fraction currently 0.6 - 0.69</p><p><b>code</b>: Guideline-based Care <span style=\"background: LightGoldenRodYellow; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid khaki\"> (<a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/uv/cpg/STU1/CodeSystem-cpg-common-process.html\">CPG Common Process</a>#guideline-based-care)</span></p><p><b>selectionBehavior</b>: one-or-more</p><p><b>definition</b>: <a href=\"PlanDefinition-VentilatedCOVID19patientsInterventionPlan-fio2-point6.html\">PEEP Intervention plan for COVID-19 patients, inspiratory oxygen fraction currently 0.6 - 0.69</a></p></blockquote><blockquote><p><b>action</b></p><p><b>title</b>: PEEP_Intervention_Plan_FiO2_0.7</p><p><b>description</b>: PEEP Intervention plan for COVID-19 patients, inspiratory oxygen fraction currently 0.7 - 0.79</p><p><b>code</b>: Guideline-based Care <span style=\"background: LightGoldenRodYellow; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid khaki\"> (<a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/uv/cpg/STU1/CodeSystem-cpg-common-process.html\">CPG Common Process</a>#guideline-based-care)</span></p><p><b>selectionBehavior</b>: one-or-more</p><p><b>definition</b>: <a href=\"PlanDefinition-VentilatedCOVID19patientsInterventionPlan-fio2-point7.html\">PEEP Intervention plan for COVID-19 patients, inspiratory oxygen fraction currently 0.7 - 0.79</a></p></blockquote><blockquote><p><b>action</b></p><p><b>title</b>: PEEP_Intervention_Plan_FiO2_0.8</p><p><b>description</b>: PEEP Inte